      <body>
         <div type="address"><address><addrLine><pb facs="0030_FL81799803"/><hi rend="pre-print">Dr. Arthur Schnitzler</hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="pre-print"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb168815">Wien XVIII.
                        Sternwartestrasse 71</rs></hi></addrLine></address><address><addrLine>Herrn Dr. <hi rend="latintype">Stefan Zweig</hi></addrLine><addrLine><rs type="place" ref="#pmb51">Wien I</rs></addrLine><addrLine><rs type="place" ref="#pmb249577"><hi rend="latintype">Kochgasse 8</hi></rs></addrLine></address></div>
         <div type="writingSession" n="1"><opener><salute><pb facs="0031_FL81799591"/>lieber Herr Doctor</salute></opener><p>danke<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>chön! Der <anchor type="commentary" xml:id="K_L03799-1"/><rs type="work" ref="#pmb296102" subtype="implied">Artikel</rs><note type="commentary" corresp="K_L03799-1"><bibl><rs type="person" ref="#pmb296098">Stanislas Rzewuski</rs>: <rs type="work" ref="#pmb296102">Arthur Schnitzler</rs>. In: <rs type="work" ref="#pmb88803">Le Figaro</rs>. Supplément Littéraire, Jg. 7, Nr. 5,
                        <date>4. 2. 1911</date>, S. 3</bibl>.</note> (von <hi rend="latintype"><rs type="person" ref="#pmb296098">Rzewuski</rs></hi>, nicht <hi rend="latintype"><rs type="person" ref="#pmb27373">Wyzewa</rs></hi>) im <hi rend="latintype"><rs type="work" ref="#pmb88803">Figaro</rs></hi> i<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t mir durch den <anchor type="commentary" xml:id="K_L03799-2"/><rs type="org" ref="#pmb29796"><hi rend="latintype">Observer</hi></rs><note type="commentary" corresp="K_L03799-2">Eine
                  Agentur für Zeitungsausschnitte. <rs type="person" ref="#pmb2121">Schnitzler</rs> hatte ein Abonnement und bekam
                  Zeitungsartikel zugesandt, die ihn mehr als nur im Nebenbei erwähnten.</note>
               zugegangen.</p><closer>Herzlich<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t Ihr<lb/><signed>A. S.</signed></closer><postscript><dateline><date>11. 2. 911</date></dateline></postscript></div>
      </body>
